Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在害怕什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要稍微試試就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Layer:02 GIRLS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CYBERIA不是你能隨便來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一萬？ 太貴了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡有市價四千的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Accela 我們是這樣稱呼它的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實成分都是差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚴格來說不算是毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到自己更快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為誰會發E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰…是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…玲音幻想出來的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要遲到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 果然是弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放過她吧 玲音很可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼事啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還有收到E-MAILl嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E-MAIL？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千砂同學寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事啊 再也沒收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音你有收到嗎？ 那惡作劇的E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是好奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 你昨晚去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔 不像啦不像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是昨天的CYBERIA有一個人跟你很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CYBERIA？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我們第一次去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實那兒沒什麼了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天還緊張的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是夜店 年輕人群聚跳舞的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在那兒看到一個跟你很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人一定不會是玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們也不是看的很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那個人穿的很時髦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很難親近加上一直生氣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟玲音個性格截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她們真的很像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下一次我們帶玲音一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要確認一下是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別鬧了 一點都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道玲音去夜店會不會變了另一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對喔 其實玲音也應該活潑一點才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的對 玲音一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會很有趣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音你也要多一點社交活動會比較快樂喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Accela 是一種新型毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是一種超微型的機械
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服食後會引起體內細胞共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誘發出一種特別的荷爾蒙激增
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種荷爾蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會使人對時間的意識受到影響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意識上時間突然加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是腦部活動組織也會受到影響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運算功能會由一倍增至十二倍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種超微型的機械藥品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個晚上就會被胃酸破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影響力便會漸漸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚一起去CYBERIA玩吧(From 亞莉絲)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人與人之間都聯繫著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來送貨的 馬上要下貨了 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請簽收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好想有一部這樣的電腦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些東西全是你的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你不知道裡面是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是最新型的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有所有的周邊配備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這麼厲害的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以自由自在地穿梭於網絡之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也常自己組裝電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但跟這就沒得比了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就不會用電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快就會的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音的電腦終於送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把東西整理好 礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸吃過飯就替你組裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這電腦很棒 我自己也很想用它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你… 立刻替我組裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 突然？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我替你裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為小孩子而設的電腦很就會過時了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「對話」這種系統是為了人與人之間的聯繫而設的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要先登記使用者名稱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用聲控吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello 電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這電腦是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以在朋友面前炫耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 美香 有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電腦 有沒有我的E-MAIL？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有玲音的E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 你在哪裡？ 大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不快來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這轉角向左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後直走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在底層
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！ 大姐 擋到路了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就說只要用這方法就能進入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情報中心的資料電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道還有別的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個比老師還厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時玲音都應該睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 你沒有合適一些的衣服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下次帶她去買成熟點的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她穿了會好看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗華
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次我們見到的不是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說了玲音是絕對不會穿成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會用那種詞彙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不會化這種妝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人真的很像我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛開始我們還以為那就是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傻丫頭還在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗華 你先扶著她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 你站著幹什麼？ 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 我在叫你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要逼我這麼做？
